members.member:
This calss is to provide the MenuItem a behaviour to show check box with toggle featue. You can define on a per-group basis the rules for checked options: 1) Exactly one option must be checked (default) 2) Zero or one option must be checked (add a ? at the end of the group name) 3) One or more options must be checked (add a + at the end of the group name) 4) Any number of options can be checked (add a * at the end of the group name). That's actually the same as not using the attached behavior at all.
